  25 Nov 2006; Charlie Shepherd <masterdriverz@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Kernel's got this one...

  02 Apr 2006; Robin H. Johnson <robbat2@gentoo.org>
  files/fdutils-5.5-destdirfix.patch, fdutils-5.5.ebuild:
  Fix usage of bindnow-flags to actually be used, fix install phase (needs to
  be serialized, not parallel), and fix glitch in destdir patch for
  install-info.

  25 Dec 2005; Diego Petten√≤ <flameeyes@gentoo.org> fdutils-5.5.ebuild:
  Use bindnow-flags function instead of -Wl,-z,now.

  16 Jul 2005; Daniel Black <dragonheart@gentoo.org>
  +files/fdutils-5.5-destdirfix.patch, fdutils-5.4.20020222-r1.ebuild,
  fdutils-5.5.ebuild:
